The paper discusses image captioning, which is a task related to computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The evaluation framework proposed in the paper focuses on assessing models for grammaticality, truthfulness, and diversity, which are topics related to machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and information retrieval (cs.IR).
